## Component Organization
```typescript
// Single component file (< 100 lines)
src/components/prayer/PrayerCard.tsx

// Multi-file component (> 100 lines)
src/components/prayer/PrayerModal/
├── index.tsx              # Main export
├── PrayerModalHeader.tsx  # Subcomponent
├── PrayerModalBody.tsx    # Subcomponent
├── usePrayerModal.ts      # Hook
└── types.ts               # Local types
```

## Naming Conventions
- **Components:** PascalCase (`PrayerCard.tsx`)
- **Hooks:** camelCase with `use` prefix (`usePrayers.ts`)
- **Utils:** camelCase (`formatDate.ts`)
- **Types:** PascalCase (`Prayer.ts` or in `types/`)
- **Constants:** SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE

## Import Order
```typescript
// 1. React and core libraries
import { useState, useEffect } from 'react';
import { motion } from 'framer-motion';

// 2. Third-party libraries
import mapboxgl from 'mapbox-gl';

// 3. Internal aliases (@/)
import { supabase } from '@/lib/supabase';
import { usePrayers } from '@/hooks/usePrayers';

// 4. Relative imports
import { PrayerCardHeader } from './PrayerCardHeader';

// 5. Types (last)
import type { Prayer } from '@/types';
```

